<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">

<head>
    {{> head }}
</head>

<body class="bg-body-bg">
    {{> preloader }}
    <div class="container-fluid p-0">
        <div class="row min-vh-100 g-0">
            <div class="col-lg-7 position-relative">
                <div class="position-absolute w-100 h-100" style="
                    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.9) 0%, rgba(118, 75, 162, 0.9) 100%),
                                url('/assets/images/gallery2.jpg');
                    background-size: cover;
                    background-position: center;
                    filter: blur(2px);
                    z-index: 1;
                "></div>
                
                <div class="position-absolute w-100 h-100 bg-dark opacity-25" style="z-index: 2;"></div>
                
                <div class="position-relative d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center h-100" style="z-index: 3;" x-data="auth">
                    <div class="w-100" style="max-width: 480px;">
                        <div class="card bg-white border-0 shadow-lg rounded-10 p-4 mx-3">
                            <div class="p-md-3 p-2">
                                <div class="text-center mb-4">
                                    <h3 class="fs-26 fw-medium text-dark" style="margin-bottom: 6px;">Registrarse</h3>
                                    <p class="fs-16 text-secondary lh-1-8">¿Ya tienes una cuenta? <a href="/accounts/login"
                                            class="text-primary text-decoration-none">Iniciar Sesión</a></p>
                                </div>

                                <form>
                                    <div class="mb-20">
                                        <label class="label fs-16 mb-2">DNI</label>
                                        <div class="form-floating">
                                            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="floatingInput1"
                                                placeholder="Ingrese su DNI *" x-model="registerForm.dni" maxlength="8">
                                            <label for="floatingInput1">Ingrese su DNI *</label>
                                            <span class="text-danger" x-text="error.dni"></span>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="mb-20">
                                        <label class="label fs-16 mb-2">Correo Electrónico</label>
                                        <div class="form-floating">
                                            <input type="email" class="form-control" id="floatingInput2"
                                                placeholder="Ingrese su correo electrónico *" x-model="registerForm.email">
                                            <label for="floatingInput2">Ingrese su correo electrónico *</label>
                                            <span class="text-danger" x-text="error.email"></span>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="mb-20">
                                        <label class="label fs-16 mb-2">Tu Contraseña</label>
                                        <div class="form-group" id="password-show-hide">
                                            <div class="password-wrapper position-relative password-container">
                                                <input type="password" class="form-control text-secondary password"
                                                    placeholder="Ingrese su contraseña *" x-model="registerForm.password">
                                                <i style="color: #A9A9C8; font-size: 22px; right: 15px;"
                                                    class="ri-eye-off-line password-toggle-icon translate-middle-y top-50 position-absolute cursor text-secondary"
                                                    aria-hidden="true"></i>
                                            </div>
                                            <span class="text-danger" x-text="error.password"></span>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="mb-20">
                                        <label class="label fs-16 mb-2">Confirmar Contraseña</label>
                                        <div class="form-group" id="password-show-hide">
                                            <div class="password-wrapper position-relative password-container">
                                                <input type="password" class="form-control text-secondary password"
                                                    placeholder="Confirmar contraseña *" x-model="registerForm.password2">
                                                <i style="color: #A9A9C8; font-size: 22px; right: 15px;"
                                                    class="ri-eye-off-line password-toggle-icon translate-middle-y top-50 position-absolute cursor text-secondary"
                                                    aria-hidden="true"></i>
                                            </div>
                                            <span class="text-danger" x-text="error.password_confirm"></span>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="mb-20">
                                        <div class="form-check">
                                            <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" value="" id="flexCheckDefault" x-model="registerForm.terms">
                                            <label class="form-check-label fs-16" for="flexCheckDefault">
                                                Acepto los <a href="#" class="text-decoration-none text-primary">Términos y condiciones</a>
                                            </label>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                    <div class="mb-3 text-center" style="width: 100%;">
                                        <span class="text-danger" x-text="error.non_field_errors" x-show="error.non_field_errors?.length > 0"></span>
                                    </div>

                                    <div class="mb-4">
                                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary fw-normal text-white w-100"
                                            style="padding-top: 18px; padding-bottom: 18px;" @click="register">Registrarse</button>
                                    </div>

                                </form>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-lg-5 d-none d-lg-flex align-items-center justify-content-center position-relative">
                <div class="text-center p-5">
                    <div class="mb-4">
                        <img src="/assets/images/register.png" alt="Imagen de Registro" class="img-fluid rounded-3 shadow-sm" style="max-width: 300px; height: auto;">
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-4">
                        <h2 class="fs-32 fw-bold text-dark mb-3">¡Únete a nosotros!</h2>
                        <p class="fs-16 text-secondary lh-1-6 mb-3">
                            Crea tu cuenta y forma parte de una comunidad comprometida con el bienestar y la seguridad de todos.
                        </p>
                        <p class="fs-14 text-muted">
                            Tu voz es importante. Regístrate y ayuda a construir un entorno más seguro para tu comunidad.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script type="module" src="/assets/js/actions/auth.js"></script>
    {{> scripts }}
</body>

</html>